<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Birthday Wishes</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f2f2f2; margin: 0; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <h1>Happy Birthday!</h1>
            <p>Warm wishes from Pacesetter Transport Services to:</p>
            <h2>{{Name}}</h2>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <p>Dear {{Name}},</p>
            <p>On behalf of everyone at Pacesetter Transport Services, I want to wish you a very happy birthday!</p>
            <p>May this special day bring you lots of joy, happiness, and wonderful surprises. We appreciate all your hard work and dedication to our team.</p>
            <p>Have a fantastic day!</p>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #777;">
            Best regards,<br>
            Pacesetter Transport Service<br>
            Managements<br>
            Pacesetter Transport Service
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
